## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="557f3-111">次の例では、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>リストをビルドする<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>国の名前を含む要素、phrase いずれかのうちの 1 つ含まれている認識を使用できます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-111">The following example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> element to build lists of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> elements containing country names, any one of which may be used to recognize the containing phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-112">この例でし、その結果のいずれかの追加<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>ヨーロッパ諸国および南アメリカ国のそれぞれの規則にオブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-112">The example then adds one of the resulting <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects to their respective rules for European countries and South American countries.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-113">さらに、この例では、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>オブジェクトへのグループ ルール参照を`ruleEurope`と`ruleSAmerica`を 2 つの方法があり、いずれか 1 つのリストにすることがありますを使用する音声指示を認識します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-113">Further on, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to group rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica` into a list of two alternatives, either one of which may be used to recognize spoken input.</span></span>  

```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  

  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  

  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  

  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  

  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  

  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  

  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  

```



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="557f3-116">次の例では、語句を認識する文法「ワールド カップが勝利した民族が」とそれに続くワールド カップが勝利した国の名前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-116">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-117">という名前のパブリック規則が作成`WorldCupWinner`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-117">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-118">2 つ作成し、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>オブジェクトを使用して<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>オブジェクトの配列を含む新しい<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-118">It then creates two <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> objects using <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects that contain arrays of new <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-119">この例で生成された文法を表示するには、次を参照してください。<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-119">To see the grammar that this example generates, see <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.%23ctor%2A>.</span></span>  

```csharp  
 public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  

  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  

  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  

  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  

  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  

  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  

  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="557f3-124">次の例では、語句を認識する文法「ワールド カップが勝利した民族が」とそれに続くワールド カップが勝利した国の名前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-124">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-125">この例では、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>要素の配列から許容国名のリストを構築する<xref:System.String>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-125">The example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> element to build lists of acceptable country names from an array of <xref:System.String> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-126">この例でし、その結果のいずれかの追加<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>ヨーロッパ諸国および南アメリカ国のそれぞれの規則にオブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-126">The example then adds one of the resulting <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> objects to their respective rules for European countries and South American countries.</span></span>  

```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
    // Create a grammar from an SRGSDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument srgsGrammar = new SrgsDocument ();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule ("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  

  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add (new SrgsItem ("A nation that has won the world cup is"));  

  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf (new string[] {"England","France","Germany","Italy"});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  

  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf (new string[] {"Argentina","Brazil","Uruguay"});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  

  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  

  // Add all the rules to the grammar and make winnerRule  
  // the root rule of the grammar.  
  srgsGrammar.Rules.Add (new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  srgsGrammar.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="557f3-131">次の例では、語句を認識する文法「ワールド カップが勝利した民族が」とそれに続くワールド カップが勝利した国の名前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-131">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-132">この例では、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>許容国からの名前の配列のリストを作成するためオブジェクト<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-132">The example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to build lists of acceptable country names from an array of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="557f3-133">使用して、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf.Add%2A>メソッド、例では、追加、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>に文字列「イタリア」を格納している、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>オブジェクト`oneOfEurope`です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="557f3-133">Using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem> that contains the string "Italy" to the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object `oneOfEurope`.</span></span>  

```  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  

  // Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  

  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  

  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"),   
    new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany")});  
  oneOfEurope.Add(new SrgsItem("Italy"));  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  

  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"),   
    new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  

  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem   
    (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  

  // Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
  // the root rule of the document.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  document.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
